{"tid":1423353,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"珠海學院近300校友師生聯署　質疑警方針對記者施暴","createTime":"2019-08-06T13:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T14:45:05.000Z","uid":71112,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e1047807b21e652b1634f89d318e83381cf45744","tid":1423353,"uid":71112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:40:11.000Z","msg":"近300名珠海學院校友師生聯署，嚴厲譴責警方以催淚彈傷害珠海一名新聞系學生，並質疑當時附近沒有示威者，警方是否針對記者施暴。<br />\n<br />\n昨日一名珠海學生身穿記者背心，在深水埗警署門外頭部受傷流血，受傷學生並無生命危險，但左眼角兩處傷口要縫三針；另一名在大公報任職記者的校友亦受警方粗暴對待。<br />\n<br />\n聯署指出，過去數星期，前線記者多次受警方言語侮辱和暴力攻擊，甚至無理拘捕，警方敵視傳媒工作，肆意踐踏新聞自由，行為令人髮指，敦促警方公開交代學生受傷的事件原因，同時要求政府成立獨立調查委員會。<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-06 HKT 19:44<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473099-20190806.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473099-20190806.htm&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2Bv%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=a596db3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473099-20190806.htm&h=a1c58aff\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473099-20190806.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n証明警察已經疲累不堪，政府就黎無招出  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8dd091c9fe3e5f6b77e6f63ae0e8502e2f2a7d","tid":1423353,"uid":71112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:43:44.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4fd6715efd5aac049598b3fc2bbda1a845bce8d9","tid":1423353,"uid":111984,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:44:24.000Z","msg":"珠大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0172b8bdace5677e4e2e080d25dcf610300bae9","tid":1423353,"uid":71112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:48:01.000Z","msg":"大公報記者都夠膽搞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3a464ac44ce496fa0afd9fe9a2dadc94f102cce","tid":1423353,"uid":7111